high_descs: Turn to the left and walk forward to the sink and then turn right.
Pick up a tomato from the counter.
Turn around and walk forward then turn to the left and face the fridge.
Place the tomato inside of the fridge and chill it. Open the fridge and take out the tomato.
Turn to the left and go forward and then make a right to walk to the microwave.
Place the tomato inside the microwave and shut the door.
Turn left, go forward, turn right and go to the counter
Pick up the tomato on the counter
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the fridge
Put the tomato in the fridge, wait, pick up the tomato
Turn left, go to the counter, turn right in front of of the microwave
Put the tomato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Cool a tomato and put it into microwave

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the dishwasher, turn to your left again and go to the counter across from you, by the stove, with the loaf of bread on it.
Pick up the tomato near the stove, on the counter.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Place the tomato in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, in front of the plate, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the tomato from the refrigerator.
Go to the microwave, on the counter, to your left.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the microwave.
